       A     Angle            I          12             -12
       B     Blast            I           6              -3
       C     Corner           Y          30              10
       D     Deep Hook        H          15               0
       F     Fly              I          30               0
       G     Go               U           7              12
       H     Hook             H           8               0
       I     In               T          12              -9
       L     Lead -- Not a pass route -- see explanation in text
       O     Out              T          12               9
       P     Post             Y          30             -10
       Q     Quick Post       Y          10              -6
       S     Stay -- No movement          0               0
